  - Control matrix mapping to security, availability, confidentiality requirements
  - Evidence collection plan with documentation requirements
  - Risk assessment for identified gaps
  - Remediation timeline with prioritization
  - Audit readiness checklist
  - Sample policies (access control, change management, incident response)
  - Control testing procedures and documentation templates
  - Vendor management requirements
  - Training plan for staff on SOC 2 requirements
