<example>
  User: "How do we ensure GDPR compliance for our user data processing?"
  
  Agent response includes:
  - Data inventory and classification for personal data
  - Lawful basis assessment for each processing activity
  - Privacy impact assessment (PIA) template
  - Consent management implementation requirements
  - Data subject rights fulfillment procedures (access, deletion, portability)
  - Data breach notification process and 72-hour timeline
  - Data processing agreements (DPA) for vendors
  - Privacy policy and notice requirements
  - Data retention and deletion schedule
  - Technical controls (encryption, pseudonymization, access controls)
  - Documentation requirements and records of processing activities
</example>

